				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "A drow heading a scouting party was killed by Halsin in bear form. The drow was tadpoled, like the player, but unlike the player he has no idea he was infected. He thinks the tadpole was the voice of his god - the Absolute - speaking to him."
